# T1082 – System Information Discovery

## Description
This technique simulates system recognition by retrieving detailed information about the host.

## Command Used
Invoke-AtomicTest T1082

## Logs Observed
- Process creation events (Event ID 4688 OR 4799)
- Execution of commands like systeminfo

## Analysis
System information gathering helps attackers understand the environment and identify potential vulnerabilities or targets.

## Detection Opportunities
- Monitor execution of systeminfo and related commands
- Detect unusual system queries
- Correlate with reconnaissance patterns

## MITRE ATT&CK Mapping
- Tactic: Discovery
- Technique: T1082
